#. ﻿DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ABBOT_0
msgid "[@]I'm Abbott, not the Mayor.[WAIT@]But with the way things are going now, I might as well be.[WAIT@]I do almost all of the work around here![WAIT@]If you want to see Mayor Goodman, go to the room to your left."
msgstr "[@]我叫阿博特，不是市长。[WAIT@]但照现在的情况来看，我倒不如说我就是市长。[WAIT@]这里几乎所有的工作都是我在做！[WAIT@]如果你想见古德曼市长，请去左边的房间。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ABBOT_2_0
msgid "[@]Hey, [Ninten]![WAIT@]How are you doing?[WAIT@]I'm thinking of running for the elections.[WAIT@]The Mayor's getting too old for his job.[WAIT@]It's about time we have someone younger in charge."
msgstr "[@]嘿，[Ninten]！[WAIT@]你在干什么？[WAIT@]我在思考参加选举的事。[WAIT@]市长年事已高，已经没法胜任这项工作了。[WAIT@]是时候让年轻人来负责了。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ABBOT_SPEAKER_Abbott
msgid "Abbott"
msgstr "Abbott"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_0
msgid "[@]Wow! That canary is singing Laura's baby.[WAIT@]Will you return her baby to her?"
msgstr "[@]哇！那只金丝雀是Laura的孩子。[WAIT@]你要还给她吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_1-OPT_0
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_1-OPT_1
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_2
msgid "[@]Great![WAIT@]Now you just have to find her.[WAIT@]If I remember correctly, Laura lives in one of the white bird houses."
msgstr "[@]太棒了！[WAIT@]你只需要找到她就行了。[WAIT@]如果我没记错，Laura住在一个白色鸟屋里。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_5
msgid "[@]You can't just keep it as a pet!"
msgstr "[@]你不能把它当宠物养！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_BABY_SPEAKER_Alfred
msgid "Alfred"
msgstr "Alfred"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_0
msgid "[@]Laura remembered her song, and began to sing once more.[WAIT@]Did you learn the melody?"
msgstr "[@]Laura想起了她的歌，并开始唱出它来。[WAIT@]你学会这段旋律了吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_1-OPT_0
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_1-OPT_1
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_2
msgid "[@]That's no good."
msgstr "[@]不是很好。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_3
msgid "[@]I heard that a long time ago, the canaries of this village didn't sing.[WAIT@]Well, that was until a man with an ocarina showed up, and started playing a lullaby to the canaries of this village.[WAIT@]There was also a woman who let her singing pet canaries loose in the village.[WAIT@]Together, they managed to turn this quiet village into a lively one."
msgstr "[@]我听说很久以前，这个村里的金丝雀不唱歌。[WAIT@]直到一个吹笛的男人出现，他为村里的金丝雀演奏了一首摇篮曲。[WAIT@]还有一个女人把她会唱歌的宠物金丝雀放到了村里。[WAIT@]他们齐心协力，把这个安静的村庄变成了一个热闹的村庄。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_SONG_SPEAKER_Alfred
msgid "Alfred"
msgstr "Alfred"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_WEATHER_0
msgid "[@]It's fine weather today.[WAIT@]But... I don't care.[WAIT@]You see, the famous Songbird Laura just lost her baby...[WAIT@]What? No, it's not dead.[WAIT@]Some jerks just stole it.[WAIT@]And now, none of the birds want to sing.[WAIT@]At this rate, no-one will want to visit Canary Village anymore..."
msgstr "[@]今天天气真好。[WAIT@]但...我不在乎。[WAIT@]你看，著名鸣鸟Laura的孩子丢了...[WAIT@]什么？不，它还没死。一些混蛋刚刚偷了它。[WAIT@]现在，没有鸟想唱歌了。[WAIT@]这样下去，没人会想参观金丝雀村庄了..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_WEATHER_SPEAKER_Alfred
msgid "Alfred"
msgstr "Alfred"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_WORK_0
msgid "[@]It might surprise you, but I don't actually work here.[WAIT@]I've been visiting this place for 30 years, and people keep asking me if they can feed the birds.[WAIT@]The answer is no, but it's still annoying."
msgstr "[@]你可能很惊讶，但实际上我不在这工作。[WAIT@]我已经来这个地方30年了，人们一直问我他们能不能喂鸟。[WAIT@]我一直拒绝，但这还是很烦人。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALFRED_WORK_SPEAKER_Alfred
msgid "Alfred"
msgstr "Alfred"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALICE_0
msgid "[@]Heya! Did you know that not only you can eat Bread, but you can also [color]turn it into Crumbs[/color]?[WAIT@]If you use the Crumbs in a fight, you can [color]instantly escape from battle[/color].[WAIT@]I heard long ago, people would use them to go back on their tracks when they got lost.[WAIT@]Though, they tended to attract bugs and cause problems, so people stopped doing that.[WAIT@]Rumor says some guy even got lost in a ghost town where everything's white."
msgstr "[@]嘿呀！你知道吗你不仅可以吃面包，你还能[color]把它们变成面包屑[/color]？[WAIT@]如果你在战斗中使用面包屑，你可以[color]立刻从战斗中逃脱[/color]。[WAIT@]我听说很久以前，我听说很久以前，当人们迷路时，他们会使用面包屑以回归正道。[WAIT@]然而，面包屑往往会吸引虫子是个问题，所以人们不再这样做了。[WAIT@]谣言说有人甚至在一个鬼城迷路了，那里一切都是白色的。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALICE_SPEAKER_Alice
msgid "Alice"
msgstr "Alice"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_0
msgid "[@]Grrr."
msgstr "[@]啊啊啊。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_SPEAKER_Alligator
msgid "Alligator"
msgstr "鳄鱼"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_THOUGHTS_1_0
msgid "[@](Honestly, you're the one who provoked me, but I forgive you.)"
msgstr "[@]（之前你确实是激怒我了，但我原谅你。）"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_THOUGHTS_1_SPEAKER_Alligator
msgid "Alligator"
msgstr "鳄鱼"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_THOUGHTS_2_0
msgid "[@](Are you angry at me? I'm sorry you feel that way.)"
msgstr "[@]（你在生我气吗？很抱歉惹你生气。）"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_ALLIGATOR_THOUGHTS_2_SPEAKER_Alligator
msgid "Alligator"
msgstr "鳄鱼"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BELLE_0
msgid "[@]This place is such an amazing deal.[WAIT@]I'll never sleep at home again."
msgstr "[@]这地方的性价比太高了。[WAIT@]我再也不会在家睡觉了。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BELLE_SPEAKER_Belle
msgid "Belle"
msgstr "靓女"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BRITANNY_0
msgid "[@]Did a poltergeist attack your house?[WAIT@]It tore mine apart."
msgstr "[@]有没有捣蛋鬼袭击你家的房子？[WAIT@]我家的房子已经被拆烂了。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BRITANNY_SPEAKER_Britanny
msgid "Britanny"
msgstr "Britanny"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BRITANNY_2_0
msgid "[@]Apparently poltergeist attacks aren't covered by insurance.[WAIT@]How dreadful..."
msgstr "[@]明显被恶作剧攻击是除外责任。[WAIT@]太可怕了..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BRITANNY_2_SPEAKER_Britanny
msgid "Britanny"
msgstr "Britanny"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BURGER_TOILET_0
msgid "[@]I bought a hamburger, but it was actually a cheeseburger.[WAIT@]The worst part is that I'm lactose intolerant."
msgstr "[@]我买了个牛肉堡，但这实际上是个芝士堡。[WAIT@]最糟的事我接受不了乳糖。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_BURGER_TOILET_SPEAKER_???
msgid "???"
msgstr "？？？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_CHICK_THOUGHTS_0
msgid "[@](Yay! Yay! I am with momma!)"
msgstr "[@]（耶！耶！我和妈妈在一起！）"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_CHICK_THOUGHTS_SPEAKER_Canary
msgid "Canary"
msgstr "金丝雀"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_SING_0
msgid "[@]This canary is singing!"
msgstr "[@]这只金丝雀在唱歌！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_SPEECHLESS_0
msgid "[@]..."
msgstr "[@]..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_SPEECHLESS_SPEAKER_Canary
msgid "Canary"
msgstr "金丝雀"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CANARY_THOUGHTS_1_0
msgid "[@](I hope Laura is doing okay.)"
