#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_CALL_0
msgid "[@]Are you okay, [Ninten]?[WAIT@]What on earth is happening to our home?[WAIT@]I'm so scared..."
msgstr "[@]你还好吗，[Ninten]?[WAIT@]我们家到底发生了什么?[WAIT@]我好害怕..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_CALL_3
msgid "[@]If only your father were here now..."
msgstr "[@]如果你爸爸在这就好了..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_CALL_6
msgid "[@]Oh! That must be him."
msgstr "[@]哦！那肯定是他。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_CALL_7
msgid "[@]Could you get it, [Ninten]?"
msgstr "[@]你要接吗，[Ninten]？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_CALL_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_FOOD_0
msgid "[@]Oh [Ninten], you're much braver than I could ever imagine.[WAIT@]You must be exhausted.[WAIT@]Here, I'll make you some [FavFood].[WAIT@]You can eat here and rest for the night."
msgstr "[@]哦[Ninten]，你比我想的要勇敢。[WAIT@]你一定累坏了。[WAIT@]在这，我将会给你做些[FavFood]。[WAIT@]你可以留下吃饭和过夜。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_FOOD_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_GOT_KEY_0
msgid "[@]Take anything you want from the basement.[WAIT@]I'm sure it will be useful to you."
msgstr "[@]你可以拿走地下室里任何你想要的东西。[WAIT@]我确信里面会有对你来说有用的东西的。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_GOT_KEY_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_KEY_0
msgid "[@]So you're leaving, huh?[WAIT@]I guess all boys have to leave home someday...[WAIT@]If you want to know where I put the [color]Basement Key[/color], I gave it to [color]Mick.[/color][WAIT@]Don't tell Mimmie, though."
msgstr "[@]你要走了，是吗？[WAIT@]我猜所有男孩都总有一天都要离开家...[WAIT@]如果你想知道我把[color]地下室钥匙[/color]放在哪里了，我把它给了[color]Mick[/color]。[WAIT@]不过，别告诉 Mimmie。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_KEY_4
msgid "[@]I made sure to keep all the Orange Juice away from her."
msgstr "[@]我得确保她不能接近任何橙汁。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_KEY_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_KEY_AGAIN_0
msgid "[@]I gave the [color]Basement Key[/color] to [color]Mick.[/color][WAIT@]Don't tell Mimmie, though.[WAIT@]I made sure to keep all the Orange Juice away from her."
msgstr "[@]我把[color]地下室钥匙[/color]给了[color]Mick[/color]。[WAIT@]不过，别告诉[Mimmie]。[WAIT@]我得确保她接近不了任何[color]橙汁[/color]。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_KEY_AGAIN_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_PANIC_0
msgid "[@]Are you okay, [Ninten]?[WAIT@]What on earth is happening to our home?[WAIT@]I'm so scared...[WAIT@]If only your father were here now..."
msgstr "[@]你还好吗，[Ninten]？[WAIT@]我们的家到底怎么了？[WAIT@]我好害怕...[WAIT@]要是你爸爸现在在就好了..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_PANIC_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_PHONE_0
msgid "[@]Telephone! [Ninten], would you please get it?"
msgstr "[@]电话！[Ninten]，你能接一下吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_PHONE_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_RESTED_0
msgid "[@]Did you have a good rest?[WAIT@]Whenever you want some more [FavFood], you're welcome to come home."
msgstr "[@]休息好了吗？[WAIT@]无论什么时候，要是你想吃[FavFood]了，尽管回家就好。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CAROL_RESTED_SPEAKER_Carol
msgid "Carol"
msgstr "Carol"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CELESTE_0
msgid "[@]Dead people don't just get up and walk for no reason.[WAIT@]I bet someone's controlling them."
msgstr "[@]死人不会无缘无故地起来游荡。[WAIT@]我敢打赌，是有人在控制他们。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CELESTE_SPEAKER_Celeste
msgid "Celeste"
msgstr "浅蓝色"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CELESTE_2_0
msgid "[@]Young man, you did well."
msgstr "[@]年轻人，你做的很好。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CELESTE_2_SPEAKER_Celeste
msgid "Celeste"
msgstr "浅蓝色"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_0
msgid "[@][Ninten] picked up the phone."
msgstr "[@][Ninten]拿起了听筒。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_1
msgid "[@][Ninten]? It's your dad.[WAIT@]Hmm, I see. Sounds like it must be a poltergeist of some sort.[WAIT@]I'm not sure what to do about it either...[WAIT@]Oh, I remember![WAIT@]Your great-grandfather studied [color]PSI[/color] at one point.[WAIT@]He documented all of his research in a [color]diary[/color] of his."
msgstr "[@][Ninten]? 这里是爸爸。[WAIT@]呣，我知道了。听起来一定是有人在恶作剧。[WAIT@]我也不知道该怎么办。[WAIT@]哦，我想起来了![WAIT@]你的曾祖父一度研究 [color]PSI[/color] 。[WAIT@]他把他所有的研究成果记录在一本[color]日记[/color] 里。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_7
msgid "[@]We put all of his junk in the [color]basement[/color], but I think it's locked.[WAIT@]The [color]key[/color] shouldn't be too far..."
msgstr "[@]我们把他所有的破烂都扔到[color]地下室[/color]去了，而我记得那里上了锁。[WAIT@]那把[color]钥匙[/color]应该不会太远..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_9
msgid "[@]Anyway, you're our only hope![WAIT@]You've always dreamed about going on an adventure, haven't you?[WAIT@]Well, go forth and protect us all, [Ninten]![WAIT@]Oh, and if you ever need to [color]SAVE your progress[/color], don't forget to [color]call your dear old dad[/color]."
msgstr "[@]无论如何，你就是我们唯一的希望了！[WAIT@]你一直梦想能去冒险，不是吗?[WAIT@]那么，去前进然后保护我们所有人吧，[Ninten]！[WAIT@]哦，如果你需要[color]存档[/color]，别忘了[color]给你亲爱的爸爸打个电话[/color]。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_13
msgid "[@](Click! Beep-beep-beep...)"
msgstr "[@]（咔嚓！ 嘟-嘟-嘟...）"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAD_POLTERGEIST_SPEAKER_Dad
msgid "Dad"
msgstr "爸爸"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVE_0
msgid "[@]Y-You aren't going to the cemetery, are you?[WAIT@]...There's word of zombies, so be careful."
msgstr "[@]你-你不是要去墓地，对吧？[WAIT@]...听说那里有丧尸，要多加小心啊。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVE_SPEAKER_Dave
msgid "Dave"
msgstr "Dave"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVE_2_0
msgid "[@]You're terrific!"
msgstr "[@]你真是了不起！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVE_2_SPEAKER_Dave
msgid "Dave"
msgstr "Dave"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVID_0
msgid "[@]I've got a weird disease where my coins keep disappearing.[WAIT@]The doctor says I have to stay away from arcades.[WAIT@]Who would've known I've got Pac-Man Fever."
msgstr "[@]我得了一种很怪的病，症状是我口袋里的硬币会一个接一个地消失不见...[WAIT@]医生给我开的处方是让我远离游戏中心。[WAIT@]可谁能想得到我还患有吃豆人狂热？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_DAVID_SPEAKER_David
