#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_MOUSE_POISON_0
msgid "[@](Be careful if you ever get [color]poisoned[/color] ([Poisoned]) out there![WAITBR]You might think it works the same as in Dragon Quest, but it's totally different![WAITBR]Instead of taking damage each turn, it'll make your [color]HP drop faster[/color] than usual after taking a hit.[WAITBR]This means you'll have to act more quickly if you've taken mortal damage.)"
